%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiddle-class-lifestyle-six-figure-salary-economy-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20today's%20big%20story%2C%20we're%20looking%20at%20people%20who%20feel%20like%20a%20middle-class%20salary%20doesn't%20equal%20a%20middle-class%20lifestyle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiddle-class-lifestyle-six-figure-salary-economy-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NIA%20Probe%20Against%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3F%20Lt%20Governor's%20New%20Claim%2C%20AAP's%20Rebuttal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20explosive%20turn%20of%20events%20Monday%2C%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20has%20called%20for%20an%20anti-terror%20probe%20into%20allegations%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20received%20political%20funding%20from%20the%20banned%20Sikhs%20For%20Justice%20group%20founded%20by%20wanted%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Pannun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20hit%20back%20swiftly%20via%20senior%20leader%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%2C%20who%20dismissed%20the%20call%20for%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20party%20and%20its%20leader.%20%26quot%3BLG%20sir%20is%20an%20agent%20of%20the%20BJP...%20This%20is%20another%20big%20conspiracy%20against%20Chief%20Minister%20Kejriwal%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20brief%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20-%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20long-running%20and%20fierce%20war%20between%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20power%20at%20the%20centre%20-%20come%20less%20than%20three%20weeks%20before%20the%20national%20capital%20votes%20in%20the%20general%20election.%20In%202019%20the%20BJP%20won%20all%20Delhi's%20seven%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20letter%20to%20the%20Union%20Home%20Secretary%2C%20Mr%20Saxena%20referred%20to%20a%20video%20(which%20he%20said%20was%20enclosed%20with%20the%20missive)%20in%20which%20Pannun%20declares%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20%26quot%3Breceived%20a%20staggering%20amount%20of%20%2416%20million%20in%20funding%20from%20Khalistani%20groups...%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Kejriwal%20purportedly%20promised%20to%20facilitate%20release%20of%20Devender%20Pal%20Bhullar%2C%20in%20return%20for%20substantial%20financial%20backing%20from%20Khalistani%20factions%20to%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party...%26quot%3B%20the%20LG's%20letter%20said%2C%20citing%20a%20complaint%20from%20a%20Hindu%20religious%20body%20and%20tweets%20by%20a%20former%20AAP%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20boss%20also%20reportedly%20received%20money%20to%20%26quot%3Bespouse%20pro-Khalistani%20sentiments%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhullar%2C%20a%20former%20professor%2C%20was%20convicted%20in%20the%201993%20Delhi%20bomb%20blasts%20case.%20In%202001%20he%20was%20given%20the%20death%20sentence%20but%20that%20was%20later%20commuted%20to%20life%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20already%20in%20jail%20over%20corruption%20charges%20linked%20to%20the%20alleged%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20that%20is%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20the%20AAP%20have%20denied%20all%20charges%2C%20labelling%20them%20acts%20of%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20vendetta%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20challenged%20his%20arrest%20-%20he%20was%20arrested%20March%2021%20-%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20He%20was%20the%20third%20top%20AAP%20leader%20to%20be%20arrested%20in%20this%20case%2C%20after%20ex-Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Sin