0Rural%20Development%20minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Alamgir%20Alam.%20Officials%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20unearthed%20the%20cash%20during%20its%20raids%20at%20half%20a%20dozen%20premises%20linked%20to%20Virendra%20Ram%2C%20former%20chief%20engineer%20at%20Jharkhand%20Rural%20Development%20Department.%20Ram%20was%20arrested%20last%20year%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20implementing%20government%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20the%20recovery%20has%20raised%20a%20political%20storm.%20The%20BJP%20has%20pointed%20to%20the%20Congress%20minister's%20connection%20and%20accused%20the%20Opposition%20party%20of%20corruption.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20is%20in%20Odisha%20for%20the%20election%20campaign%2C%20referred%20to%20the%20cash%20haul.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20mountains%20of%20currency%20notes%20are%20being%20found%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20state%20Jharkhand.%20Now%20tell%20me%2C%20if%20I%20stop%20their%20theft%2C%20their%20earning%2C%20their%20loot%2C%20won't%20they%20abuse%20Modi%20or%20not%3F%20Despite%20abuses%2C%20Shouldn't%20I%20be%20doing%20this%20work%3F%20Shouldn't%20I%20be%20saving%20your%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%2C%20countering%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20on%20the%20Centre's%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20probe%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20BJP%20chief%20Babulal%20Marandi%20said%20that%20if%20this%20is%20the%20recovery%20from%20the%20house%20of%20the%20help%20of%20a%20minister's%20secretary%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20would%20be%20found%20in%20ministers'%20homes%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThey%20keep%20saying%20ED%20is%20harassing%20us.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20government%20and%20Kalpana%20Soren%2C%20you%20should%20remove%20Alamgir%20Alam%20as%20minister%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Ms%20Soren%20is%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren's%20wife%20and%20has%20entered%20active%20politics%20after%20his%20arrest%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Alam%20has%20said%20no%20one%20should%20reach%20conclusions%20before%20the%20ED%20completes%20its%20investigation.%20He%20has%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20Sanjiv%20Lal%20had%20served%20as%20a%20secretary%20to%20two%20former%20ministers.%C2%A0%26quot%3BSanjiv%20Lal%20is%20a%20government%20employee.%20He%20is%20my%20personal%20secretary.%20Sanjiv%20Lal%20has%20already%20been%20a%20personal%20secretary%20of%20two%20former%20ministers.%20We%20usually%20appoint%20personal%20secretaries%20based%20on%20experience.%20It%20is%20not%20right%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20raids%20before%20the%20ED%20investigation%20is%20completed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714997760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fl1gc3718_ed-counting_625x300_06_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F12-hours-6-machines-rs-30-crore-and-counting-ranchis-huge-cash-haul-5601149%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20six%20cash%20counting%20machines%20are%20working%20non-stop%20to%20give%20a%20number%20to%20the%20mountain%20of%20cash%20recovered%20from%20a%20room%20in%20Jharkhand%20capital%20Ranchi%20during%20a%20raid%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F12-hours-6-machines-rs-30-crore-and-counting-ranchis-huge-cash-haul-5601149%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F12-hours-6-machines-rs-30-crore-and-counting-ranchis-huge-cash-haul-5601149%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F12-hours-6-machines-rs-30-crore-and-counting-ranchis-huge-cash-haul-5601149%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Camera%2C%20%26quot%3BRarest%20Of%20The%20Rare%26quot%3B%20Confrontation%20Between%20Tigress%2C%20Bear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWild%20encounters%20are%20the%20most%20sought%20after%20by%20wildlife%20enthusiasts%20as%20well%20as%20tourists.%20One%20such%20video%20is%20going%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20which%20shows%20a%20bear%20coming%20face-to-face%20with%20a%20tigress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20shared%20by%20a%20retired%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20Dr%20Ravi%20Gupta%20has%20captured%20%26quot%3Brarest%20of%20the%20rare%26quot%3B%20sights%20between%20a%20tigress%20and%20a%20bear%20in%20Pilibhit%20Tiger%20Reserve%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20the%20tigress%20is%20seen%20taking%20a%20majestic%20stroll%20along%20a%20woodland%20road%20in%20the%20dense%20forest%2C%20as%20tourists%20on%20safari%20jeeps%20witness%20the%20sight%20from%20a%20distance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bear%20suddenly%20appears%20from%20the%20bushes%20and%20crosses%20in%20front%20of%20the%20tigress.%20The%20tigress%20takes%20a%20moment%2C%20pauses%20and%20settles%20down%20seeing%20the%20bear%20crossing%20the%20path%2C%20the%20video%20shows%2C%20attentively%20observing%20the%20bear's%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tigress%20keenly%20watches%20the%20bear%2C%20rather%20keeping%20an%20eye%20out%20for%20the%20bear%20after%20it%20crosses%20the%20street%20and%20goes%20to%20the%20opposite%20side.%20And%20then%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20in%20a%20rare%20act%20of%20aggression%2C%20the%20bear%20attacks%20the%20tigress%2C%20sparking%20a%20brief%20confrontation%20between%20the%20two%20formidable%20predators.%20Despite%20the%20unexpected%20standoff%2C%20the%20tigress%20maintains%20calmness%20and%20poise.%20The%20tigress%20watches%20the%20bear%20as%20it%20departs%20after%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20rarest%20of%20rare%20sight%20of%20a%20bear%20charging%20towards%20a%20tigress%2C%20captured%20today%20at%20Pilibhit%20T