id%20she%20would%20carry%20a%20statue%20of%20Lord%20Ganesh%20with%20her%20on%20the%20commercial%20crew%20flight%20as%20%26quot%3BGanesh%20is%20her%20good%20luck%20charm%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20she%20was%20happy%20to%20have%20Lord%20Ganesh%20with%20her%20in%20outer%20space.%20On%20her%20earlier%20trips%20to%20space%2C%20she%20carried%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20her%20other%20passions%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20is%20a%20marathon%20runner%20and%20has%20run%20a%20marathon%20while%20she%20was%20at%20the%20International%20Space%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20she%20nervous%20before%20her%20third%20flight%3F%20She%20said%20that%20although%20she%20is%20a%20bit%20anxious%2C%20she%20has%20no%20jitters%20about%20flying%20in%20a%20new%20spacecraft.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20reach%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20it%20will%20be%20like%20returning%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20space%2C%20she%20broke%20a%20few%20records%20-%20a%20major%20one%20being%20the%20time%20when%20she%20used%20to%20hold%20the%20record%20for%20maximum%20spacewalk%20time%20by%20a%20female%20astronaut.%20She%20took%20seven%20spacewalks%2C%20totalling%2050%20hours%20and%2040%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20currently%20training%20to%20pilot%20the%20Crew%20Flight%20Test%20mission%20aboard%20Boeing's%20Starliner%20spacecraft%20-%20the%20vehicle's%20first%20crewed%20flight.%20Sunita%20Williams%20was%20selected%20to%20be%20an%20astronaut%20in%201998%20and%20was%20chosen%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20select%20group%20of%20astronauts%20to%20fly%20on%20NASA's%20commercial%20crew%20program%20after%20the%20Space%20Shuttle%20was%20retired%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714994040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-02%2Fsunita-williams_650x400_51486668310.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fwhat-sunita-williams-carries-to-space-as-her-lucky-charm-5600710%22%2C%22summary%22%3A