ancial-services-124050600628_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wipro's%20new%20GenAI-powered%20cognitive%20assistants%20will%20operate%20on%20Microsoft%20Azure%20Open%20AI%20and%20will%20be%20accessible%20through%20Azure%20App%20Services%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fwipro-microsoft-team-up-for-ai-virtual-assistants-for-financial-services-124050600628_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fwipro-microsoft-team-up-for-ai-virtual-assistants-for-financial-services-124050600628_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fwipro-microsoft-team-up-for-ai-virtual-assistants-for-financial-services-124050600628_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Intense%20Coral%20Bleaching%20Recorded%20In%20Lakshadweep%20Due%20To%20Marine%20Heatwave%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResearchers%20at%20the%20ICAR-Central%20Marine%20Fisheries%20Research%20Institute%20(CMFRI)%20have%20recorded%20widespread%20bleaching%20affecting%20the%20coral%20reefs%20in%20the%20Lakshadweep%20Sea%20due%20to%20marine%20heatwaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20from%20several%20Lakshadweep%20islands%20showed%20that%20a%20considerable%20percentage%20of%20the%20hard%20coral%20species%20have%20undergone%20severe%20bleaching%2C%20primarily%20due%20to%20a%20prolonged%20period%20of%20marine%20heatwave%20affecting%20the%20region%20since%20late%20October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarine%20heatwaves%20are%20rare%20extreme%20weather%20events%20that%20involve%20prolonged%20periods%20of%20abnormally%20high%20ocean%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20temperatures%20often%20exceed%20the%2090th%20percentile%20of%20typical%20regional%20ocean%20temperatures%20based%20on%20historical%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Lakshadweep%2C%20the%20Degree%20Heating%20Week%20(DHW)%20indicator%2C%20which%20measures%20accumulated%20heat%20stress%2C%20has%20surged%20above%204%20degrees%20Celsius-weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration%20(NOAA)%2C%20this%20level%20of%20DHW%20poses%20a%20substantial%20risk%20of%20coral%20bleaching%2C%20threatening%20the%20region's%20diverse%20marine%20ecosystems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20KR%20Sreenath%2C%20senior%20scientist%20of%20CMFRI%20said%20such%20heat%20stress%20levels%20signify%20a%20severe%20threat%20to%20coral%20health%2C%20leading%20to%20extensive%20bleaching%20where%20corals%20lose%20the%20symbiotic%20algae%20(zooxanthellae)%2C%20compromising%20their%20survival%20by%20depriving%20them%20of%20essential%20nutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20DHW%20continues%20to%20rise%2C%20reaching%20beyond%2012%20degrees%20Celsius%20weeks%2C%20it%20could%20precipitate%20an%20unprecedented%20biodiversity%20crisis%20due%20to%20multispecies%20mortality%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Sreenath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dr%20Shelton%20Padua%2C%20senior%20scientist%20at%20CMFRI%2C%20the%20primary%20causes%20of%20these%20marine%20heatwaves%20as%20excessive%20heat%20atmospheric%20transfer%20coupled%20with%20shifts%20in%20ocean%20currents%2C%20leading%20to%20unusually%20high%20water%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20October%2027%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Lakshadweep%20Sea%2C%20spanning%20from%2080.0%20to%2012.0%20N%20latitude%20and%2071.0%20to%2075.0%20E%20longitude%2C%20has%20been%20experiencing%20these%20conditions%2C%20with%20temperatures%20consistently%20registering%20rises%20greater%20than%201%20degree%20Celsius%20above%20the%20norm%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Padua.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViewing%20that%20the%20health%20of%20marine%20ecosystems%20is%20integral%20to%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20coastal%20communities%2C%20influencing%20tourism%20and%20fisheries%20sectors%2C%20Dr%20Sreenath%20said%20that%20the%20ongoing%20marine%20heatwaves%20are%20likely%20to%20cause%20significant%20economic%20losses%20by%20disrupting%20their%20vital%20ecosystem%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeath%20and%20disintegration%20of%20coral%20reefs%20can%20threaten%20the%20coastal%20communities%2C%20leaving%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20impacts%20of%20sea%20level%20aggressions%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Dr%20Sreenath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECMFRI%20has%20been%20actively%20undertaking%20studies%20to%20better%20understand%20ecological%20changes%20affecting%20coral%20reefs%20besides%20initiating%20a%20comprehensive%20national%20project%20aimed%20at%20investigating%20the%20resilience%20potential%20of%20various%20coral%20reefs%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714993440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F2r43oqr8_lakshadweep-mmt_625x300_08_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fintense-coral-bleaching-recorded-in-lakshadweep-due-to-marine-heatwave-5600420%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Researchers%20at%20the%20ICAR-Central%20Marine%20Fisheries%20Research%20Institute%20(CMFRI)%20have%20recorded%20widespread%20bleaching%20affecting%20the%20coral%20reefs%20in%20the%20Lakshadweep%20Sea%20due%20to%20marine%20heatwaves.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fintense-coral-bleaching-recorded-in-lakshadweep-due-to-marine-heatwave-5600420%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fintense-coral-bleaching-recorded-in-lakshadweep-due-to-marine-heatwave-5600420%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fintense-coral-bleaching-recorded-in-lakshadweep-due-to-marine-heatwave-5600420%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C