%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20engaged%20in%20an%20unexpected%20battle%20of%20words%20over%20the%20batter's%20'strike-rate'%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024.%20Gavaskar%20has%20been%20regularly%20criticising%20Kohli%20over%20his%20inability%20to%20get%20into%20ulra-attacking%20mode%20and%20rescue%20RCB's%20campaign.%20However%2C%20Virat%20decided%20to%20hit%20back%20at%20all%20those%20criticising%20him%20over%20his%20strike-rate%2C%20but%20little%20did%20he%20expect%20that%20the%20cricketer-turned-commentator%20Gavaskar%20would%20be%20sharp%20with%20his%20reply%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20there%20continues%20to%20remain%20a%20back-and-forth%20between%20Kohli%20and%20Gavaskar%2C%20former%20Australia%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Matthew%20Hayden%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F219-matthew-hayden-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMatthew%20Hayden%3C%2Fa%3E%20jumped%20into%20the%20debate%2C%20saying%20he%20expects%20nothing%20but%20fireworks%20from%20Virat%20at%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20strike%20rate%20is%20trending%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%20it's%20trending%20up.%20Look%20at%20the%20IPL%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20it's%20gone%20from%20mid%20and%20around%20that%20120%20then%20it%20goes%20130%20and%20then%20140%20and%20150.%20So%20150%20for%20me%20is%20kind%20of%20that%20sweet%20spot%20that%20starts%20in%20and%20everyone%20having%20conversation%20well%20where%20you%20bat%3F%20Is%20it%20three%2C%20is%20it%20open%3F%20You%20know%20those%20first%20six%20overs%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20if%20Kohli%20is%20in%20those%20first%20six%20overs.%20You%20know%20that%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20fireworks%2C%26quot%3B%20Hayden%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHayden%20feels%20the%20support%20Kohli%20would%20have%20in%20the%20Indian%20team%20would%20be%20much%20better%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20squad%20he%20has%20at%20RCB.%20Hence%2C%20there%20shouldn't%20be%20doubt%20over%20Kohli's%20potential%20performances%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20also%20know%20that%20these%20conditions%20that%20are%20going%20to%20be%20in%20the%20West%20Indies.%20They're%20not%20so%20sure%20about%20those%20conditions%20in%20New%20York.%20I've%20seen%20that%20overlaid%20venue%20and%20it%20looks%20magnificent.%20But%20certainly%20through%20the%20West%20Indies%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20benign%20conditions%20and%20Kohli%20is%20going%20to%20come%20in%20and%20look%20to%20strike%20away%20knowing%20that%20he%20has%20a%20superb%20batting%20side%20that%20also%20has%20a%20great%20strike%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20Hayden%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714993380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fn81hf5po_virat-kohli-orange-cap-bcci_625x300_05_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fmatthew-haydens-fireworks-remark-on-virat-kohli-amid-sunil-gavaskars-criticism-5598700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%20recently%20criticised%20Virat%20Kohli%20on%20live%20TV%20for%20his%20angry%20rant%2C%20slamming%20commentators%20and%20pundits%20questioning%20his%20strike-rate%20in%20IPL%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20facing%20'disaster'%20of%20hung%20Parliament%2C%20warns%20Rishi%20Sunak%20after%20local%20election%20debacle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714993373000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109885700%2Cimgsize-840607.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-facing-disaster-of-hung-parliament-warns-rishi-sunak-after-local-election-debacle%2Farticleshow%2F109885700.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftim