eservation%20as%20needed%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20backwards%2C%20Dalits%20and%20adivasis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20come%20amid%20a%20high-pitched%20campaign%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20heated%20exchanges%20between%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20on%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20plans%20to%20tinker%20with%20the%20reservation%20for%20backward%20classes%20to%20benefit%20Muslims.%20The%20Congress%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations.%20At%20a%20rally%20in%20Gujarat%20Banaskantha%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20challenge%20the%20'shehzada'%20of%20the%20Congress%20as%20well%20as%20his%20party%20and%20its%20supporters%20to%20announce%20they%20will%20never%20misuse%20reservation%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%2C%20nor%20will%20they%20play%20with%20the%20Constitution%20or%20grant%20reservation%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Ratlam%20rally%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20media%20does%20not%20show%20news%20related%20to%20atrocities%20on%20Adivasis.%20%26quot%3BYour%20children%20are%20raped%2C%20your%20land%20is%20snatched%2C%20but%20media%20does%20not%20report.%20There%20is%20a%20reason.%20There%20are%20no%20Adivasis%20in%20these%20media%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20said%2090%20bureaucrats%20run%20the%20country's%20government.%20%26quot%3BThey%20distribute%20the%20budgets.%20Only%201%20out%20of%20the%2090%20is%20an%20Adivasis%2C%20three%20are%20from%20backward%20classes%2C%20three%20from%20the%20Dalit%20community.%20Your%20people%20are%20neither%20in%20the%20media%20nor%20the%20corporate%20world.%20We%20want%20to%20change%20this.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20caste%20Census%20and%20an%20economic%20survey%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr