ith%20murder%20of%20an%2018-year-old%20woman%20who%20was%20stabbed%20more%20than%20120%20times%20in%20her%20suburban%20Chicago%20home%20almost%20six%20decades%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fman-79-charged-over-1966-illinois-murder-after-dna-breakthrough-13129244%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fman-79-charged-over-1966-illinois-murder-after-dna-breakthrough-13129244%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fman-79-charged-over-1966-illinois-murder-after-dna-breakthrough-13129244%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IFS%20Officer%20Transformed%20a%20Barren%20UP%20Land%20into%20His%20District%E2%80%99s%201st%20Eco-Tourism%20Hub%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20(IFS)%20officer%20Vikas%20Nayak%20saw%20the%20land%20where%20Rapdi%20Eco%20Tourism%20Centre%20stands%20today%2C%20he%20saw%20immense%20potential.%20Sitting%20barren%20right%20next%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F95718%2Fyamuna-river-pollution-scientists%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERiver%20Yamuna%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20place%20was%20a%20deserted%20land%20with%20dying%20biodiversity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20something%20about%20the%20land%20which%20made%20me%20want%20to%20conserve%20biodiversity.%20When%20I%20saw%20the%20place%2C%20I%20could%20envision%20a%20spot%20much%20more%20than%20a%20barren%20plot.%20I%20immediately%20started%20to%20draw%20a%20plan%20with%20my%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConceptualised%20in%202023%2C%2011%20months%20later%2C%20Vikas%20was%20able%20to%20build%20Rapdi%20Ecotourism%20Centre%20along%20with%20his%20team.%20%E2%80%9COn%20its%20opening%20day%2C%20we%20had%20about%201%2C100%20people%20swarming%20the%20place%2C%20which%20is%20a%20lot%20for%20a%20place%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20muses%20Vikas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20attempting%20to%20save%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20place%20was%20a%20key%20factor%2C%20there%20was%20another%20reason%20to%20rejuvenate%20the%20place%20%E2%80%94%20spreading%20awareness%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282775%2Frobinson-crusoe-worlds-remotest-island-to-document-conserve-biodiversity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econscious%20tourism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20ravine%20experience%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20a%20short%20drive%20away%20from%20Shikohabad%20in%20the%20district%20of%20Firozabad%2C%20the%20place%20is%20home%20to%20hundreds%20of%20trees%2C%20wooden%20huts%2C%20boats%20and%20a%20lot%20more%20and%20was%20%E2%80%9Ctaken%20up%20to%20create%20the%20first%20ecotourism%20facility%20in%20the%20district.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20first%20posted%20in%20the%20area%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20it%20did%20not%20have%20any%20ecotourism%20place.%20The%20locals%20were%20not%20very%20active%20in%20natural%20conservation%20either%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20officer%20started%20to%20look%20around%20the%20area%20and%20found%20the%20perfect%20place%20here%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20perfect%20place%20as%20it%20had%20ravine%20qualities%20and%20also%20a%20little%20elevation.%20I%20got%20down%20to%20drawing%20plans%20and%20making%20a%20budget.%20We%20formulated%20a%20project%20and%20presented%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337165%2Fstartup-leopard-tech-lab-helps-kerala-forest-department-combat-wildlife-crime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20the%20forest%20departments%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Esecuring%20funding%20for%20its%20implementation.%20Following%20the%20funding%20acquisition%2C%20which%20was%20in%20March%202023%2C%20we%20started%20the%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20place%20has%20a%20plethora%20of%20activities%20including%20a%20trek%20and%20boating.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349019%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20place%20has%20a%20plethora%20of%20activities%20including%20a%20trek%20and%20boating.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20place%20was%20completed%20and%20opened%20to%20the%20public%20without%20a%20fee%20in%20February%202024.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20was%20also%20made%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20Agra%20%E2%80%94%20which%20attracts%20a%20lot%20of%20tourists%20%E2%80%94%20is%20nearby.%20This%20ensures%20that%20the%20place%20might%20get%20more%20visitors%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Vikas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ecotourism%20centre%20has%20a%20plethora%20of%20activities%20besides%20the%20biodiversity%20and%20lush%20greenery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20includes%20a%20%E2%80%98geo%20trek%E2%80%99%2C%20wooden%20cottages%20for%20visitors%20to%20book%20and%20stay%2C%20speed%20boating%2C%20bird%20watching%20spots%2C%20cave%20explorations%2C%20a%20butterfly%20park%20and%20a%20cafeteria%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Vikas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20incorporated%20some%20elevated%20features%2C%20resembling%20a%20hillside%20terrain%2C%20and%20developed%20geo%20treks%20for%20exploration.%20Additionally%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20established%20butterfly%20spots%20where%20visitors%20can%20learn%20about%20the%20forest%20and%20river%20ecosystems.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESetting%20up%20and%20running%20an%20ecotourism%20centre%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20area%20became%20an%20eco-tourism%20centre%2C%20Vikas%20informs%20that%20the%20place%20was%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20them%20and%20dacoits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20with%20planting%20trees%20in%20the%20areas%20and%20improving%20the%20place%E2%80%99s%20greenery.%20We%20also%20set%20up%20habitats%20for%20birds%20and%20butterflies.%20Although%20the%20place%20had%20many%20trees%2C%20we%20started%20to%20plant%20more%20and%20build%20the%20place%20around%20the%20trees.%20The%20design%20was%20such%20that%20it%20did%20not%20disrupt%20the%20existing%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%20wanted%20to%20create%20and%20attract%20more%20tourists%20to%20the%20area%2C%20and%20he%20also%20wanted%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20eco%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298606%2Fecosphere-encourages-sustainable-tourism-in-spiti-solar-power-homestays-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponsible%20tourism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20forest%20department%20to%20involve%20locals%20in%20the%20work.%20From%20helping%20with%20maintaining%20the%20forests%20to%20setting%20up%20such%20projects%20to%20rescuing%20wildlife%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20tradition%20for%20the%20department%20to%20seek%20help%20from%20the%20local%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20this%20tradition%2C%20Vikas%20mapped%20out%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20help%20the%20local%20community%20grow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Guests%20can%20stay%20at%20the%20mud%20homes%20at%20the%20eco%20tourism%20centre.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349020%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGuests%20can%20stay%20at%20the%20mud%20homes%20at%20the%20eco-tourism%20centre.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20facility%2C%20which%20is%20now%20fully%20operational%2C%20benefits%20the%20local%20community%20by%20providing%20opportunities%20for%20them%20to%20manage%20the%20canteen%2C%20parking%20facilities%2C%20and%20collecting%20the%20entry%20fees.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20are%20conducting%20hospitality%20training%20to%20ensure%20quality%20service%20for%20visitors%2C%20including%20guidance%20on%20serving%20food%20and%20interacting%20during%20nature%20treks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EA%20committee%20has%20been%20established%20to%20oversee%20the%20facility%E2%80%99s%20management%2C%20with%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20proceeds%20going%20to%20the%20government%20as%20royalty%20and%20the%20rest%20being%20allocated%20to%20the%20community%2C%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20place%20is%20a%20100%20percent%20plastic%20free%20zone.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20allowing%20any%20plastic%20inside%20the%20park.%20We%20are%20also%20working%20with%20SHGs%20and%20sourcing%20local%20art%20pieces%20such%20as%20jute%20bags%20and%20wooden%20art%20pieces%20to%20sell%20to%20the%20visitors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20the%20clientele%20for%20this%20ecotourism%20venture%20is%20unique%2C%20consisting%20of%20individuals%20who%20understand%20and%20appreciate%20responsible%20tourism%20practices.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20responsible%20tourist%2C%20one%20must%20recognise%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20and%20minimise%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336460%2Fiit-kanpur-startup-kinoko-biotech-founder-chaitanya-dubey-innovates-biodegradable-thermocol-fertilizer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20environmental%20impact.%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20ecotourism%2C%20facilities%20may%20be%20limited%2C%20but%20the%20emphasis%20is%20on%20sustainability%20and%20immersion%20in%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohit%2C%20who%20travelled%20from%20Shikohabad%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20the%20eco-park%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20came%20with%20my%20family%20to%20explore%20the%20ecotourism%20centre.%20The%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20very%20new%20concept%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20place%20of%20recreation.%20It%20is%20really