%20they%20could%20enjoy%20a%20steady%20daily%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20understanding%20the%20nitty%20gritty%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fsari-history-celebration-of-culture-on-republic-day-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaree%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ankush%20finally%20quit%20his%20high-paying%20job%20in%202021%20and%20launched%20Deeva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20a%20small%20village%20to%20Shark%20Tank%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20start%20Deeva%2C%20Ankush%20exhausted%20all%20his%20savings%20of%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20and%20an%20additional%20Rs%203%20lakh%20financial%20support%20from%20his%20father.%20Much%20against%20his%20hopes%2C%20he%20experienced%20extreme%20losses.%20Amid%20societal%20pressure%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20Chennai%20%E2%80%94%20where%20he%20pursued%20his%20higher%20education%20%E2%80%94%20to%20escape%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ankush%20says%20his%20success%20is%20rooted%20in%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20clothing%20legacy.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%