ption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20heartwarming%2C%20Ankeet%20and%20Girish%20express%2C%20that%20the%20parents%20who%20were%20once%20lost%20in%20the%20chaos%2C%20are%20now%20confident%20that%20they%20can%20overcome%20anything.%20The%20duo%20urge%20them%20to%20make%20themselves%20at%20home%20and%20recall%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20setting%20up%20%E2%80%94%20figuring%20out%20which%20utensils%20they%20must%20have%3B%20which%20amenities%20are%20needed%20and%20finding%20a%20caretaker%20as%20well.%20It%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259309%2Fmumbai-teen-entrepreneur-startup-seekh-learning-tool-for-toddlers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20learning%20curve%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20just%20for%20the%20duo%20but%20also%20for%20the%20families.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20come%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20rural%20India%20where%20they%20cook%20using%20firewood.%20Some%20of%20them%20have%20never%20operated%20a%20gas.%20So%2C%20we%20had%20to%20teach%20them%20how%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ankeet.%20The%20duo%20still%20recall%20when%20on%20the%20first%20day%2C%20one%20parent%20enquired%20if%20there%20was%20farmland%20nearby.%20%E2%80%9CObviously%2C%20there%20wasn%E2%80%99t.%20We%20then%20understood%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20relieve%20himself%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20use%20the%20bathroom%20in%20the%20house%2C%20which%20we%20quickly%20taught%20him.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20safe%20space%20for%20the%20little%20bravehearts%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20settled%20in%20and%20the%20friend%20duo%20was%20happy%20that%20accommodation%20was%20a%20big%20load%20taken%20off%20their%20minds.%20But%2C%20the%20months%20ahead%20revealed%20the%20necessity%20of%20a%20holistic%20solution.%20In%20time%2C%20they%20began%20supplying%20groceries%20to%20the%20centre%2C%20encouraging%20the%20families%20to%20cook%20according%20to%20their%20dietary%20and%20regional%20preferences%20and%20also%20launched%20the%20transport%20arm%20of%20Access%20Life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20Ankeet%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20these%20families%20did%20not%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20go%20to%20and%20fro%20from%20the%20hospital%20to%20the%20centre.%20While%20they%20would%20resort%20to%20public%20transport%2C%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20ideal%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311164%2Fst-jude-india-childcare-centres-gives-holistic-cancer-care-to-underprivileged-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20who%20were%20undergoing%20chemotherapy%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20their%20private%20vehicles%20ensure%20the%20children%20and%20their%20parents%20can%20travel%20in%20comfort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-4-1714469540.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20of%20Access%20Life%2C%20an%20initiative%20that%20provides%20multidisciplinary%20services%20to%20children%20who%20have%20cancer%20and%20their%20families%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-4-1714469540.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-4-1714469540-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-4-1714469540-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-4-1714469540-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-4-1714469540-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20of%20Access%20Life%2C%20an%20initiative%20that%20provides%20multidisciplinary%20services%20to%20children%20who%20have%20cancer%20and%20their%20families%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ankeet%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20families%20are%20cared%20for%20well%20here%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20they%20have%20a%20life%20waiting%20for%20them%20back%20in%20their%20respective%20villages.%20What%20happens%20to%20that%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Access%20Life%E2%80%99s%20Emotional%20and%20Psychological%20Support%20(EPS)%20programme%20comes%20in.%20It%20equips%20families%20with%20practical%20ways%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20distress%20created%20by%20the%20disease.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20keeping%20the%20children%20engaged%20with%20educational%20sessions%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20miss%20out%20on%20school%2C%20and%20teaching%20the%20parents%20new%20skills%20that%20could%20be%20a%20source%20of%20livelihood%20when%20they%20return%20to%20their%20respective%20hometowns%20after%20their%20child%E2%80%99s%20long%20treatment%2C%20the%20duo%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20one%20example%2C%20Ankeet%20recalls%20the%20example%20of%20a%20parent%20who%20used%20to%20run%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259515%2Findian-food-recipes-pakora-map-of-india-cuisine-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epuri%20bhajiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E(a%20fast%20food%20stall)%20stall%20in%20Siliguri%2C%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20came%20to%20live%20at%20our%20centre%20for%20his%20child%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20(which%20lasted%20six%20months)%2C%20he%20had%20to%20sell%20his%20cart%20back%20home.%20He%20was%20worried%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20his%20livelihood.%20But%20during%20his%20time%20here%2C%20he%20learnt%20how%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20started%20selling!%20The%20business%20was%20a%20huge%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGirish%20pitches%20in%20with%20another%20heartwarming%20story.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20parents%20was%20a%20soldier%20who%20quit%20and%20came%20to%20our%20Mumbai%20centre%20when%20his%20child%20was%20admitted.%20But%20in%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed%2C%20he%20saw%20how%20well%20his%20son%20was%20being%20cared%20for%20at%20the%20centre.%20That%20enabled%20him%20to%20go%20back%20to%20his%20duty%20peacefully.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20duo%20encourages%20both%20parents%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20child%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20they%20are%20aware%20that%20this%20is%20not%20always%20possible%20and%20are%20always%20willing%20to%20make%20exceptions.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20a%20family%20that%20has%20two%20kids%20and%20one%20is%20admitted%20here%20and%20the%20other%20is%20an%20infant%2C%20we%20ask%20the%20family%20to%20bring%20both%20kids%20so%20they%20can%20all%20live%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Girish%20shares.%20They%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20comfort%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327071%2Fvaranasi-ias-officer-himanshu-nagpal-mission-muskaan-reunites-lost-children-with-families%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20families%3C%2Fa%3E%20trumps%20everything%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20navigate%20this%20challenge%2C%20it%20is%20reassuring%20to%20know%20that%20someone%20is%20looking%20out%20for%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECancer%20warrants%20a%20certain%20trepidation%2C%20a%20certain%20tiptoeing%2C%20a%20certain%20foreboding.%20But%20the%20laughter%20and%20happy%20chatter%20at%20the%20Access%20Life%20centres%2C%20disagree.%20For%20anyone