024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20project%20will%20ensure%20that%20these%20handrickshaw%20pullers%20will%20get%20the%20funds%20to%20buy%20e-rickshaws%20which%20will%20help%20ease%20their%20task%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348643%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20project%20will%20ensure%20that%20these%20handrickshaw%20pullers%20will%20get%20the%20funds%20to%20buy%20e-rickshaws%20which%20will%20help%20ease%20their%20task%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sunil%20Shinde%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20how%20does%20this%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20an%20individual%20invests%20in%20a%20certain%20project%20on%20our%20platform%2C%20the%20money%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20investee%20via%20a%20regulated%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ram%20explains.%20He%20adds%20that%20Rang%20De%20is%20regulated%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20has%20their%20NBFC-P2P%20(Non-Banking%20Financial%20Company)%20licence%20in%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20allows%20any%20Indian%20to%20lend%20money%20to%20a%20fellow%20Indian%20over%20the%20internet%20through%20our%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20money%20is%20invested%2C%20a%20lot%20ensues%20behind%20the%20scenes%20for%20the%20funds%20to%20meet%20its