.%20Sometimes%20Deep%20and%20I%20act%20as%20the%20animal%20rescue%20team.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99d%20agree%20that%20Devaki%20is%20a%20lucky%20girl.%20Not%20many%20are%20fortunate%20to%20grow%20up%20away%20from%20the%20chokehold%20of%20technology%20but%20instead%20surrounded%20by%20paddy%20fields%2C%20flower%20beds%2C%20and%20streams.%20In%202020%2C%20when%20Kavita%20and%20Manoj%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342247%2Fmangaluru-man-quits-corporate-career-for-farming-exotic-fruits-vegetables-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equit%20their%20corporate%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Kavita%20was%20working%20with%20Vodafone%20and%20Manoj%20with%20HDFC%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20sceptical%20about%20how%20this%20would%20change%20the%20trajectory%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20in%20hindsight%2C%20they%20see%20it%20as%20the%20best%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CDevaki%20appreciates%20everything%20we%20do%20for%20the%20land%2C%20including%20growing%20our%20own%20vegetables.%20She%20is%20exposed%20to%20so%20many%20new%20things%3B%20topics%20that%20go%20beyond%20traditional%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Kavita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhomestay_11zon-1714390404.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Parijaat%20Goa%20homestay%20is%20a%20sustainable%20property%20in%20Goa's%20Anjuna%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhomestay_11zon-1714390404.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhomestay_11zon-1714390404-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhome